snippet.title: Happy Birthday Amber
snippet.description:
Happy Birthday Channel is a participant in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program, an affiliate advertising program designed to provide a means for sites to earn advertising fees by advertising and linking to Amazon products on their website. https://amzn.to/30hfoOp Make someone happy with a gift voucher from Amazon.



 https://www.facebook.com/singhappybirthday/ 

 Is someone you know having a birthday? Why not send them a personalised 'Happy Birthday' wish. 
 We have 1000s of recordings in our library, and if we don't have your name then please let us know so we can record it for you. 

 Just leave us a comment or send us a message. 

 Simply search for your friend's name then share it with them on Facebook or Twitter, via Email, WhatsApp or any other way. 

 Don’t forget to subscribe to us and see how many of your friends' names you can find to send them their very own personalised greeting. 

 Like us on Facebook for party ideas and fun things to do! 

 Lyrics Happy Birthday Song to Amber 

 Happy birthday to You 
 Happy birthday to You 
 Happy birthday Dear Amber 
 Happy birthday to you
